#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:1
msgid "CRM (`lu_mcp_crm`)"
msgstr "CRM (`lu_mcp_crm`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:3
msgid "**8 tools** for Odoo CRM lead and opportunity management."
msgstr "Odoo CRM 리드 및 영업 기회 관리를 위한 **8가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `crm` app."
msgstr "필수: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `crm` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools cover the CRM pipeline: browse stages, search leads and "
"opportunities, view the pipeline summary table, read full record details,"
" create and update leads, convert a lead to an opportunity, and post "
"internal notes."
msgstr ""
"이 도구들은 CRM 파이프라인을 다룹니다: 스테이지 탐색, 리드 및 영업 기회 검색, "
"파이프라인 요약 테이블 보기, 전체 레코드 상세 정보 읽기, 리드 생성 및 업데이트, "
"리드를 영업 기회로 전환, 내부 메모 게시."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:17
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:19
msgid "`crm_list_stages`"
msgstr "`crm_list_stages`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:21
msgid "List all CRM pipeline stages in sequence order."
msgstr "모든 CRM 파이프라인 스테이지를 순서대로 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "*(없음)*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:27 ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:51
#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:68 ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:81
#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:100 ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:119
#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:134 ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:153
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:28
msgid "*\"What are the CRM pipeline stages?\"*"
msgstr "*\"CRM 파이프라인 스테이지가 무엇입니까?\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:32
msgid "`crm_list_pipeline`"
msgstr "`crm_list_pipeline`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:34
msgid ""
"Show the CRM pipeline as a summary table grouped by stage (count + "
"expected revenue per stage). Use `crm_search_leads` to get individual "
"records."
msgstr ""
"CRM 파이프라인의 Markdown 요약 테이블을 스테이지별로 가져옵니다: 스테이지 | 건수 | 예상 매출. "
"개별 레코드를 가져오려면 `crm_search_leads`를 사용하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`user_id`"
msgstr "`user_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Filter by salesperson."
msgstr "영업담당자별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`stage_id`"
msgstr "`stage_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Filter to a specific stage."
msgstr "특정 스테이지로 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:42
msgid "Returns a Markdown table:"
msgstr "Markdown 테이블을 반환합니다:"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:52
msgid "*\"Give me a summary of the CRM pipeline for salesperson #5.\"*"
msgstr "*\"영업담당자 #5의 CRM 파이프라인 요약을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:56
msgid "`crm_search_leads`"
msgstr "`crm_search_leads`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:58
msgid "Search CRM leads and opportunities as individual records."
msgstr "리드 및 영업 기회를 검색합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`query`"
msgstr "`query`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Keyword search in name or description."
msgstr "이름 또는 설명에서 키워드 검색."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`type`"
msgstr "`type`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`'lead'` or `'opportunity'`."
msgstr "`'lead'` 또는 `'opportunity'`."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Filter by stage."
msgstr "스테이지별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Maximum results (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "최대 결과 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:69
msgid "*\"Find all opportunities in the 'Proposal' stage.\"*"
msgstr "*\"'Proposal' 스테이지의 모든 영업 기회를 찾으세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:73
msgid "`crm_read_lead`"
msgstr "`crm_read_lead`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:75
msgid "Get full details of a CRM lead or opportunity."
msgstr "리드 또는 영업 기회의 전체 상세 정보를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "`id`"
msgstr "`id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Lead or opportunity ID."
msgstr "리드 또는 영업 기회 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:82
msgid "*\"Show me the details for lead #88.\"*"
msgstr "*\"리드 #88의 상세 정보를 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:86
msgid "`crm_create_lead`"
msgstr "`crm_create_lead`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:88
msgid "Create a new CRM lead."
msgstr "새 리드를 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`name`"
msgstr "`name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Lead title."
msgstr "리드 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`partner_id`"
msgstr "`partner_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Customer partner ID."
msgstr "고객 파트너 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`'lead'` (default) or `'opportunity'`."
msgstr "`'lead'`(기본값) 또는 `'opportunity'`."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Initial pipeline stage."
msgstr "초기 파이프라인 스테이지."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Salesperson user ID."
msgstr "영업담당자 사용자 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`expected_revenue`"
msgstr "`expected_revenue`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "number"
msgstr "number"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Expected revenue amount."
msgstr "예상 매출 금액."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`description`"
msgstr "`description`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Lead description (Markdown)."
msgstr "리드 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:101
msgid ""
"*\"Create an opportunity titled 'Enterprise contract — Acme Corp' with "
"expected revenue $50,000, assigned to salesperson #3.\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"'Enterprise contract — Acme Corp'이라는 제목의 영업 기회를 생성하고 예상 매출 "
"$50,000으로 영업담당자 #3에 할당하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:105
msgid "`crm_update_lead`"
msgstr "`crm_update_lead`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:107
msgid "Update an existing lead or opportunity."
msgstr "기존 리드 또는 영업 기회를 업데이트합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Lead/opportunity ID."
msgstr "리드/영업 기회 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "New stage."
msgstr "새 스테이지."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "New salesperson."
msgstr "새 영업담당자."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`probability`"
msgstr "`probability`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Win probability (0–100)."
msgstr "성약 확률(0~100)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Updated expected revenue."
msgstr "업데이트된 예상 매출."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "`date_deadline`"
msgstr "`date_deadline`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "New deadline (`YYYY-MM-DD`)."
msgstr "새 마감일(`YYYY-MM-DD`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "New description (Markdown)."
msgstr "새 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:120
msgid "*\"Update lead #88 — move to 'Won' stage and set probability to 100.\"*"
msgstr "*\"리드 #88 업데이트 — 'Won' 스테이지로 이동하고 확률을 100으로 설정.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:124
msgid "`crm_convert_to_opportunity`"
msgstr "`crm_convert_to_opportunity`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:126
msgid ""
"Convert a lead into an opportunity. Sets the type to `opportunity` and "
"optionally links a customer partner."
msgstr ""
"리드를 영업 기회로 전환합니다. 유형을 `opportunity`로 설정하고 선택적으로 고객 파트너를 연결합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Lead ID to convert."
msgstr "전환할 리드 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md
msgid "Customer partner ID to link."
msgstr "연결할 고객 파트너 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:135
msgid ""
"*\"Convert lead #88 to an opportunity and link it to partner #15 (Acme "
"Corp).\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"리드 #88을 영업 기회로 전환하고 파트너 #15(Acme Corp)에 연결하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:138
msgid ""
"If the lead is already an opportunity, the tool returns a message "
"indicating no action was taken."
msgstr ""
"리드가 이미 영업 기회인 경우, 도구는 조치가 취해지지 않았음을 나타내는 메시지를 반환합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:144
msgid "`crm_log_note`"
msgstr "`crm_log_note`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:146
msgid ""
"Post an internal note on a lead or opportunity (not visible to the "
"customer)."
msgstr "리드 또는 영업 기회에 내부 메모를 게시합니다(고객에게 표시되지 않음)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "`body`"
msgstr "`body`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:137
msgid "Note body (Markdown)."
msgstr "메모 본문(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/crm.md:154
msgid ""
"*\"Add an internal note to opportunity #88: 'Called the procurement lead "
"— decision expected by end of month.'\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"영업 기회 #88에 내부 메모 추가: 'Procurement lead에 전화함 — 월말까지 결정 예상.'\"*"

